00:46:08.250 --> 00:46:12.140
Okay, the OpenPlay is a networking API.

00:46:12.140 --> 00:46:16.900
It's designed to be
protocol and OS independent.

00:46:16.900 --> 00:46:21.600
That means that it currently
runs under Mac OS X,

00:46:21.690 --> 00:46:25.700
Mac OS, Windows,
and as of a few days ago,

00:46:25.700 --> 00:46:28.660
Linux and some various Unix.

00:46:30.560 --> 00:46:32.580
