this to your application.

00:47:38.200 --> 00:47:39.520
There's the three layers.

00:47:39.520 --> 00:47:40.970
They all sit within OpenPlay.

00:47:40.970 --> 00:47:43.160
NetSprocket uses the protocol module.

00:47:43.160 --> 00:47:46.030
The protocol uses the net module.

00:47:46.260 --> 00:47:50.040
And then your application can use
any one or all three of those,

00:47:50.040 --> 00:47:54.960
as well as the underlying
raw protocol APIs.

